Identity Distance for a matrix

calcIdenDist.Rd

Identity Distance for a matrix

calcIdenDist(matrix)

Arguments

matrix

a matrix

Examples

set.seed(1)
x = matrix(rnorm(100), ncol = 10)
calcIdenDist(x)
